  </video>
  <steps>
    <step num="0">Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C). </step>
    <step num="1">In a bowl, mix butter, garlic, lemon juice, salt, and pepper. </step>
    <step num="2">Lay salmon fillets on a pan, and evenly distribute the marinade. </step>
    <step num="3">Place broccoli on both sides of the salmon, and drizzle on olive oil, salt, pepper, and parmesan. </step>
    <step num="4">Bake 18 minutes. </step>
    <step num="5">Serve and garnish with parsley. </step>
    <step num="6">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
